    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="prose section">
    <h2>Review questions</h2>
    <p>Self-check before or after the graded quiz below:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Why does writing to <code>counterA</code> ever affect a thread that only ever reads or writes <code>counterB</code>?</li>
      <li>What observable difference distinguishes false sharing from a data race, in both symptom and fix?</li>
      <li>Why does the JMH example need <code>@Group</code>/<code>Scope.Group</code> rather than two independent single-threaded benchmarks?</li>
      <li>Give one situation where adding padding would make performance worse, not better.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

